title: Lunchbox Calls Out Sick to Businesses He Doesn’t Work At + Name That Bass Line Game + Callers On The Craziest Places They’ve Been Trapped
itunes:title: Lunchbox Calls Out Sick to Businesses He Doesn’t Work At + Name That Bass Line Game + Callers On The Craziest Places They’ve Been Trapped
description:
Lunchbox calls out sick to businesses…the only problem is they are all places he doesn’t actually work. We play a game where we have to guess the song just by the bass guitar part. Bobby takes callers on the craziest places they’ve been trapped!
